\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {3}{\ignorespaces Average $\kappa $ (top) and predicted portfolio volatility (bottom) over 2012--2025. Confidence drops sharply during high-volatility regimes (2015--16 China shock, 2018 rate fears, 2020 COVID, 2022 rate cycle), confirming that the error characterisation correctly identifies when to trust model output less.}}{4}{figure.caption.5}\protected@file@percent }
\newlabel{fig:kappavol}{{3}{4}{Average $\kappa $ (top) and predicted portfolio volatility (bottom) over 2012--2025. Confidence drops sharply during high-volatility regimes (2015--16 China shock, 2018 rate fears, 2020 COVID, 2022 rate cycle), confirming that the error characterisation correctly identifies when to trust model output less}{figure.caption.5}{}}
